<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7431433>
    dc:description "FIGURES 74─83. Habitus, dorsal view (left) and lateral view (right). 74, 75, Fuminana diaphana sp. nov., holotype male. 76, 77, Fuminana guaricica sp. nov., holotype male. 78, 79, Fuminana incurvata sp. nov., holotype male. 80, 81, Fuminana niluga sp. nov., holotype male. 82, 83, Fuminana retorta sp. nov., holotype male. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7431433/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7431420>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1─13. Fuminana diaphana sp. nov., holotype male. 1, head and thorax, dorsal view. 2, head, frontal view. 3, head and thorax, lateral view. 4, forewing. 5–13, male terminalia: 5, sternite VIII, ventral view. 6, valve, ventral view. 7, pygofer, valve, and subgenital plate, lateral view. 8, subgenital plate, ventral view. 9, connective, dorsal view. 10, style, dorsal view. 11, style, lateral view, and enlarged portion of apex in posterior view. 12, aedeagus, lateral view. 13, aedeagus, posterior view. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7431420/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7431422>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14─26. Fuminana guaricica sp. nov., holotype male. 14, head and thorax, dorsal view. 15, head, frontal view. 16, head and thorax, lateral view. 17, forewing. 18–26, male terminalia: 18, sternite VIII, ventral view. 19 valve, ventral view. 20, pygofer, valve, and subgenital plate, lateral view. 21, subgenital plate, ventral view. 22, connective, dorsal view. 23, style, dorsal view. 24, style, lateral view, and enlarged portion of apex in posterior view. 25, aedeagus, lateral view. 26, aedeagus, posterior view. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7431422/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7431426>
    dc:description "FIGURES 35─47. Fuminana incurvata sp. nov., holotype male. 35, head and thorax, dorsal view. 36, head, frontal view. 37, head and thorax, lateral view. 38, forewing. 39–47, male terminalia: 39, sternite VIII, ventral view. 40 valve, ventral view. 41, pygofer, valve, and subgenital plate, lateral view. 42, subgenital plate, ventral view. 43, connective, dorsal view. 44, style, dorsal view. 45, style, lateral view, and enlarged portion of apex in posterior view. 46, aedeagus, lateral view. 47, aedeagus, posterior view. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7431426/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7431428>
    dc:description "FIGURES 48─60. Fuminana niluga sp. nov., holotype male. 48, head and thorax, dorsal view. 49, head, frontal view. 50, head and thorax, lateral view. 51, forewing. 52–60, male terminalia: 52, sternite VIII, ventral view. 53 valve, ventral view. 54, pygofer, valve, and subgenital plate, lateral view. 55, subgenital plate, ventral view. 56, connective, dorsal view. 57, style, dorsal view. 58, style, lateral view, and enlarged portion of apex in posterior view. 59, aedeagus, lateral view. 60, aedeagus, posterior view. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7431428/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7431439>
    dc:description "FIGURES 84─85. Prothoracic legs. 84, Fuminana incurvata sp. nov., holotype male. 85, Fuminana guaricica sp. nov., paratype male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7431439/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7431424>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27─34. Fuminana guaricica sp. nov., paratype female. 27, apical portion of abdomen, ventral view. 28, apical portion of abdomen, lateral view. 29, first valvifer and first valvula, lateral view. 30, enlarged view of dorsal sculptured area. 31, second valvula, lateral view. 32, enlarged view of teeth of dorsal margin. 33, second valvifer and gonoplac, lateral view. 34, enlarged view of apical portion of gonoplac. Scales in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7431424/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

